===========================

1. Create a directory for the project:

mkdir PopDaBalloons
cd PopDaBalloons

2. Extract tarball

tar xf popdaballoons-gdx.tgz

3. Checkout master

git checkout .

4. Get get required libraries

./setup.sh

5. Startup eclipse and select File->Import and select 
   all three projects my-gdx-game*

6. Edit the properties to fix location of the physics-body-editor library.

7. Edit the properties of catchdastars-desktop and make sure under Java Build 
   Path the Source folder catchdastars-desktop/assets points to the correct
   location.
